== 0.Intangamarara ==
Akahise ka Brarudi gafatanye n'akahise k'uburundi. kuva uburundi bukiri mubukoroni gushika bwikukire. 

Brarudi yamye iterera mw'iterambere hamwe no gusangira ibihe vy'umunezero w'abarundi biciye mubinyobwa vyayo.

ubwa mbere mu Burundi hakora INTERBRA ( société y'ababirigi aho umunyamutahe mukuru yari ibanki BRUXELLES Lambert) yadadanza ibiyeri ( Primus) vyo mu Bukavu ( ex Zaïre ) hamwe n'inzoga yitwa Carlserbg yaza ivuye Mu Bubirigi , Brasserie yaje kubaho mu [[Tel:1955|1955]] kw'izina rya Brasserie Rwanda-Urundi.

le 23/12 / [[Tel:1955|1955]] Primus yambere niho yasohorwa ikozwe na Brasserie ya Usumbura.

